    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "CAUTION:\n\u2022 Be sure to clean drain plug and install with new washer.\n  Drain plug: 29 - 39 N\u00b7m (3.0 - 4.0 kg-m, 22 - 29 ft-lb)\n\u2022 Use recommended engine oil (API SG grade).",
